'''虐待'''是某人對其他[[人|人]]或[[動物|動物]]在[[心理|心理]]或[[身體|身體]]上造成傷害的行為活動。在現代文明社會，各國就法理上對虐待行為的定義有不同。一般而言，虐待是一種犯罪行為，可被[[法律|法律]]起訴，並要受到相關懲罰。<ref>{{cite dictionary|url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/abuse|title=Abuse – Defined at Merriam-Webster Dictionary|publisher=Merriam-Webster, Incorporated|year=2013|origyear=Word first used in 15th century|quote=abuse [may be defined as the following]...to treat (a person or animal) in a harsh or harmful way...[or] to use or treat (something) in a way that causes damage [or] to use (something) wrongly|accessdate=28 December 2013|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418220631/https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/abuse|dead-url=no}}</ref>

